    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/0e0201b057a17a97e938073600664f16.poster.avif?t=1728934683\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/0e0201b057a17a97e938073600664f16.webm?t=1728934683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/0e0201b057a17a97e938073600664f16.mp4?t=1728934683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frosty Cookie clicker with a mad dash of ice cold humour, hit the targets by slinging snowy balls of fury and hurl chunks of ice and snow at targets whilst dodging the narrators commentary, Earn treasure by scoring higher and use it to unlock new content such as maps, modifiers and cosmetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowpult is a relaxing score attack cookie clicker where you take your shots and hope the narrator doesn't make a snowman out of you when you miss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/c47fe882df6dff828f20f8f8316ad032.poster.avif?t=1728934683\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/c47fe882df6dff828f20f8f8316ad032.webm?t=1728934683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019730/extras/c47fe882df6dff828f20f8f8316ad032.mp4?t=1728934683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock achievements as you reach higher scores and dscover hidden messages from the games narrator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- filled with frostbitten humour and gameplay</p>",
